┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                          SETUP PHASE                                │
│  Teacher creates account → Logs in as Teacher                      │
└────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                                 │
                                 ▼
┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    TEACHER: CREATE QUIZ                             │
│  1. Upload Questions PDF → System extracts text                    │
│  2. Review/Edit questions in UI                                    │
│  3. Upload Answer Key PDF → System extracts answers                │
│  4. Set passing score, time limit, point values                    │
│  5. Save quiz → Students can now access it                         │
└────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                                 │
                                 ▼
┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    STUDENT: TAKE QUIZ                               │
│  1. Student logs in → Sees available quizzes                       │
│  2. Selects quiz → Answers questions                               │
│  3. Submits for grading                                            │
└────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                                 │
                                 ▼
┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    AUTOMATIC GRADING                                │
│  1. System compares answers to teacher's answer key                │
│  2. Calculates score (points per question)                         │
│  3. Generates feedback with corrections                            │
│  4. Saves attempt to JSON storage                                  │
└────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                                 │
                                 ▼
┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    RESULTS & FEEDBACK                               │
│  Student views:                                                    │
│  • Score and percentage                                            │
│  • Which answers were wrong                                        │
│  • Correct answers with explanations                               │
│  • Option to review or retake                                      │
└────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘